8 March 2011Members of the media are advised that the Deputy Minister of Performance Monitoring and Evaluation in the Presidency, Ms Dina Pule will visit Provincial Executive Councils. The aim of the visits is to raise awareness about the mandate of the Department of Performance Monitoring and Evaluation as well as the role of the Deputy Minister within the Department.The visits are scheduled as follows:Wednesday, 9 March 2011 09h00-11h00: Mpumalanga Executive Council Premier s Office, Government Complex, NelspruitMedia invited for a media briefing starting from 11h15Wednesday, 16 March 2011 (TBC) Kwa-Zulu Natal Executive CouncilThursday, 17 March 2011 14h00: Free State Executive Council Lebohang Building, BloemfonteinMedia invited for a media briefing starting from 16h20Tuesday, 29 March 2011 14h00: Gauteng Executive Council Premier s Office, JohannesburgMedia invited for a media briefing starting from 16h20RSVP: Send SMS to Pheliswa Sebati on Cell: 082 413 4609Enquiries: Bongiwe Gambu Cell: 082 714 9463Issued by: Government Communication and Information System